Interface IMoodockUIView

      • registerObserver

        void registerObserver()
        Instantiate an observable cache (extends Observable implements ICacheable) Add the activity as an observer. If it is already registered, it is not added a second time. This method will be called just before the MoodockUiHelper creation.
